			<abstract>
				<p>Testimony of 30-year-old K. D. on her arrest right after the German occupation in March 1944 and her experiences in the Kistarcsa
					internment camp and the Auschwitz and St. Gheorgenthal concentration camps.</p>
			</abstract>
